query:
SELECT 
  MIN(CAST(cmlNumber AS UNSIGNED)) as min_cml,
  MAX(CAST(cmlNumber AS UNSIGNED)) as max_cml,
  COUNT(DISTINCT cmlNumber) as distinct_count,
  COUNT(*) as total_count
FROM tmlReadings 
WHERE cmlNumber IS NOT NULL 
  AND cmlNumber REGEXP '^[0-9]+$';
